  "name": "RPlog_Extraction_Race",
  "title": "Extraction Race on Nar Shaddaa",
  "summary": "On the Smuggler's Moon, NRI agent Lon tends to his wounded betrothed Siren as the city-moon descends into chaos following the death of two crime lords. Luke Skywalker and his Sullustan apprentice Ikihsa Enb'Zik veil themselves in the Force and pilot a borrowed speeder to the couple's hideout above a corner restaurant, arriving just as the battle overhead begins raining debris on the streets. The Jedi extract Lon and Siren amid scattering looters and grasping bounty hunters, with Luke deflecting blaster fire and easing Siren's pain through the Force while Zik flies a breakneck descent. After sacrificing the speeder in a controlled crash and grappling the couple onto the roof of the Side Deck, the four reunite atop the building. The escape ends on an uneasy note as a pair of black-armored guards appear on the rooftop, leaving the group's fate in the hands of their unseen contact Kaitlin.",
